<div class="row">
    <h3 style="font-family: 'Book Antiqua'"><b>Tips on buying flight tickets through Nordic Airlines</b></h3>
    <hr style="border-color:darkgray" />
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h4>How far ahead should you book a flight?</h4>
        <p>
            According to the global flight data from 2019, the best period to buy a ticket is 21 days
            prior to the departure. But also keeping an eye about the ticket prices is a good idea
            in order to find the best possible and suitable deal.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h4>What day of the week is the best to buy a ticket on Nordic Airlines?</h4>
        <p>
            The best day to buy a ticket on discount is every Sunday, when there is no need to enter
            a special code in order to get a discount. The discount is immediately being calculated when
            picking the wanted destination.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h4>How can I find a last-minute flight?</h4>
        <p>
            When you're looking for that perfect last-minute getaway, all you have to do is check out the available
            deals at Expedia. These deals will show up in green above the final price per night for hotel offerings,
            highlighting how much you'll save when you book for any time in the next two weeks.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h4>How can I get the booked flight ticket?</h4>
        <p>
            Every time you book a flight via Nordic Airlines, it is automatically sent to your provided email address.
            This way you can download it on your computer and print it if you want, or you can just download it on your
            smartphone and use it directly from there, this way you won't need to print it.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h4>How can I get a cheap last-minute flight?</h4>
        <p>
            For travelers who want to get the most affordable last-minute hotel room possible, flexibility matters
            most. If you can be more flexible regarding the exact dates you want to travel, as well as the
            destination itself, you'll have a better time finding the best deals.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h4>How can I save money on flights?</h4>
        <p>
            Buying a ticket long time prior departure can help you save money. That way you may find a ticket
            for your wanted destination on a quite low price.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>


